    "description": {
        "en-US": "The MailHops add-on will add a bar to the top of the message pane and also add a Country column to show the location of the sender.  \n\nFrom there you can click on the location and view a map of the IP hops that a message took to get to your inbox.  Distance is also calculated to give you the miles or kilometers that a message traveled.  It will also show the senders weather if you add a DarkSky API key.  User agent, DKIM and other Authentication used by the sender.  Filter by country origin, mark as junk if the message took too long or is from a country you don't trust.\n\nThis is a freemium add-on and works without paying but you can purchase an API key to unlock more features."
    },
